{"analytics_identifier":"OT1340","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market","content_id":"b1123ceb-77e4-40fc-9526-83ad0ba7cf01","description":"The Office for the Internal Market (OIM) supports the effective operation of the UK’s internal market, and provides expert and independent advice to the UK government and devolved governments. OIM is part of the Competition and Markets Authority .","details":{"acronym":"OIM","alternative_format_contact_email":"general.enquiries@cma.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Office for the Internal Market (OIM) supports the effective operation of the UK’s internal market, and provides expert and independent advice to the UK government and devolved governments.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Office for the Internal Market\">OIM</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/competition-and-markets-authority\">Competition and Markets Authority</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-business-trade","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Office for the Internal Market","image":{"alt_text":"Office for the Internal Market","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61375a748fa8f503c6403da1/OIM_GOVUK_logo_2.png"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"},{"href":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Service","href":"https://www.gov.uk/cma-cases/review-of-the-interaction-between-the-market-access-principles-and-englands-air-quality-domestic-solid-fuels-standards-regulations-2020","image":{"alt_text":"Review of the interaction between the Market Access Principles and England’s Air Quality (Domestic Solid Fuels Standards) Regulations 2020’ within ‘Office for the Internal Market (en)","high_resolution_url":"https://